" map alt+BS to delete word
cnoremap <BS> <C-w>
cnoremap <M-BS> <C-w>
cnoremap <C-BS> <C-w>
" delete word forward
cnoremap d <S-right><C-w>
cnoremap <C-d> <S-right><C-w>
" map alt+b to previous word
cnoremap b <S-left>
cnoremap <C-b> <S-left>
" map alt+f to previous word
cnoremap f <S-right>
cnoremap <C-f> <S-right>

